PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Product Discovery App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What is the app designed for?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app helps you discover exciting new products across various categories like tech, fashion, home goods, and more. It curates the latest product launches to help you stay ahead of trends.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How does the product discovery work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: We use advanced algorithms to analyze product data from thousands of brands and retailers. Based on your preferences, we surface the most relevant and innovative new offerings.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What kind of products can I find?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: You'll find a diverse range of products spanning electronics, clothing, home decor, kitchen appliances, beauty products, and more. We aim to cover all major consumer product categories.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is the app free to use?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, our product discovery app is completely free to download and use. We make money through affiliate partnerships when users make purchases discovered through our app.
